Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.57,0:00:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.53,0:00:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.32,0:00:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,attained everything this world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.33,0:00:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before\Nhis death drove people to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.04,0:00:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.83,0:00:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.92,0:00:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men head for the Grand Line\Nin pursuit of their dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.68,0:00:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly\Nentered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.81,0:00:35.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.13,0:00:40.92,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.94,0:00:47.05,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.07,0:00:52.69,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.71,0:00:58.44,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever,\NI take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.46,0:01:06.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it's not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.60,0:01:16.21,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.23,0:01:21.59,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard\Nsomeone else's biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.61,0:01:25.18,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn't there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.20,0:01:30.81,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.83,0:01:36.32,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.34,0:01:42.59,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand do you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.61,0:01:47.94,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.96,0:01:54.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.89,0:01:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The drawbridge is coming down!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.07,0:02:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they pulled through. Good timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.29,0:02:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm trembling with anticipation!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.05,0:02:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.49,0:02:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna rescue you for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.54,0:02:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lower that bridge already.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.42,0:02:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He looks evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.34,0:02:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you're a bad guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.51,0:02:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.18,0:02:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being stuck out here for all to see...\NAre you really strong at all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.18,0:02:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind your own business!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.06,0:02:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously... just because I teamed\Nup with Luffy, I've come this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.82,0:02:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Ways of Men!\NZoro's Techniques, Usopp's Dream"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.01,0:03:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still as weak as ever, Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.43,0:03:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promised her...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.15,0:03:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't afford to die in a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.08,0:03:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You again? You sure have lots of free time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.08,0:03:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll untie you, so join my crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.75,0:03:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.92,0:03:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for people to join my pirate crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.25,0:03:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it! Me, stooping to a\Ncriminal's level?! Screw that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.76,0:03:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with being a pirate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.72,0:03:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates are despicable! As if I'd wanna be one!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.10,0:04:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on! You're already\Nknown as an evil bounty hunter!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.60,0:04:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People can say whatever they want,\Nbut I ain't done anything I regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.53,0:04:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will live through this\Nand accomplish what I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.92,0:04:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.28,0:04:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've decided you're gonna join me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.83,0:04:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit deciding on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.50,0:04:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you use swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.58,0:04:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. But that stupid son took my stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.58,0:04:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'll go get it back for you!\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.80,0:04:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So if you want your sword, join my crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.89,0:04:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really getting on my nerves!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.14,0:04:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he planning to bust into the base by himself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.39,0:04:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After him! Don't let him escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.60,0:04:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! There's someone\Nin the crucifixion yard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.14,0:04:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.86,0:04:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's one traitor after the other...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.36,0:04:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please escape, Zoro-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.41,0:04:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be killed for doing that, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.12,0:04:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand to watch\Nthe Navy like this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.83,0:05:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be an honorable marine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.91,0:05:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! I can't escape! I only got ten days until--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.88,0:05:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to be executed tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.30,0:05:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.30,0:05:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Helmeppo never once intended\Nto honor your agreement!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.80,0:05:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Luffy-san got angry and punched him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.60,0:05:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.89,0:05:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy is after Luffy-san now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.73,0:05:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't ask you to be a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.02,0:05:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But please, help Luffy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.86,0:05:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san is the only one who can save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.66,0:05:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I think you're also the only\None who can save Luffy-san now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.67,0:05:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,End of the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.14,0:06:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is some interesting\Nstuff you guys've pulled!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.93,0:06:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you two and that straw hat kid\Nplannin' a coup or something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.40,0:06:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always fought alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.48,0:06:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike arrogant bastards like you\Nwho use soldiers as cronies!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.70,0:06:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roronoa Zoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.74,0:06:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare underestimate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.43,0:06:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may be strong, but before my\Nauthority, you're as good as scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.84,0:06:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aim!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.96,0:06:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.42,0:06:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...can't afford to die here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.64,0:06:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still as weak as ever, Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.13,0:06:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.52,0:06:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.48,0:06:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.77,0:06:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What are you--?!\N--Luffy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.12,0:07:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.61,0:07:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.16,0:07:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you I was strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.79,0:07:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.92,0:07:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Monkey D. Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.44,0:07:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man who's gonna be King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.72,0:07:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The King of the Pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.80,0:07:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you even know what that means?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.39,0:07:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King of the Pirates is King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.81,0:07:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are there any other meanings?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.06,0:07:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was shocked, too! But Luffy-san\Nis serious! That's how he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.44,0:07:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He intends to become the King of the Pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.44,0:07:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and obtain this world's\Nultimate treasure... the One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.66,0:07:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.91,0:07:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is yours? I couldn't tell,\Nso I brought three of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.75,0:07:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All three are mine. I use the Three-Sword Style.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.34,0:08:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll take 'em, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.51,0:08:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we fight together now, you'll be\Na government-defying villain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.93,0:08:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you prefer that, or being\Nkilled by the Navy like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.68,0:08:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, the devil's son?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.93,0:08:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever. I'll be your pirate,\Nif I'm just gonna die here instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.23,0:08:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurray! So you'll join my crew?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.69,0:08:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Woo-hoo! This is great! Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.28,0:08:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Now untie these stupid ropes already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.62,0:08:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What... is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.12,0:08:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He flung the bullets back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.37,0:08:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's no ordinary human, that Straw Hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.04,0:08:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Must've eaten one of\Nthose rumored Devil Fruits!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.67,0:08:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Devil Fruit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.96,0:08:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.38,0:08:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! These knots are tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.76,0:08:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Quit wastin' time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.63,0:08:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter who they are, everyone\Nwho opposes me gets executed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.06,0:08:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If guns won't work, then chop them to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.69,0:08:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, that's weird! It got tighter instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.36,0:09:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a damn sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.04,0:09:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.16,0:09:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roronoa Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.25,0:09:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.36,0:09:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move and you're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.05,0:09:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.80,0:09:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be a pirate. I promise you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.93,0:09:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm officially a criminal,\Nnow that I've fought the Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.73,0:09:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll tell you this right now.\NI'm only going to fulfill my ambition!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.83,0:09:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ambition?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.19,0:09:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be the world's greatest swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.44,0:09:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I wind up having to give that up,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.82,0:09:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'd better accept responsibility\Nand apologize to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.12,0:09:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world's greatest swordsman?\NThat sounds great!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.62,0:09:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The King of the Pirates would\Nneed no less than that on his crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.63,0:10:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure talk big.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.54,0:10:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this point, whether it's\Nas a criminal or whatever else,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.30,0:10:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will spread my name throughout the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.18,0:10:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you standing around for?!\NSlaughter them this instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.89,0:10:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duck, Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.52,0:10:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.02,0:10:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You did it! Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.82,0:10:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.99,0:10:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ate the Gum-Gum Fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.78,0:10:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum Fruit?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.45,0:10:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A rubber person!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.03,0:10:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he does have Devil Fruit powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.50,0:10:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! We don't stand a chance against them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.87,0:10:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These guys are crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.33,0:10:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't even handle Zoro by himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.21,0:10:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a direct order!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.01,0:10:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone who spouted weakness just now
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.88,0:10:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,must now shoot themselves in the head!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.84,0:10:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no need for weakling soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.52,0:10:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These troops are mental!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.85,0:11:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.31,0:11:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crush this navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.57,0:11:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rankless, low-status bums have\Nno right whatsoever to defy me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.37,0:11:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Navy Captain "Axe-Hand" Morgan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.38,0:11:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Luffy! Nice to meetcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.04,0:11:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.56,0:11:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-The captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.22,0:11:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Runt...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.76,0:11:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.99,0:11:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.03,0:11:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Captain Morgan is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.11,0:11:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...being trounced completely...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.41,0:11:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you call yourself a navy?!\NYou've destroyed Coby's dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.87,0:12:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, Straw Hat! Check this out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.09,0:12:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said hold it! Are you stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.59,0:12:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pay attention! I have a hostage here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.88,0:12:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Helmeppo-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.43,0:12:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.93,0:12:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you value this guy's life, don't move!\NOne move and I'll shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.80,0:12:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san! I don't want to get in\Nyour way! Even if it means dying!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.14,0:12:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.47,0:12:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it up, stupid son!\NCoby really is ready to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.87,0:12:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move! I told you not to move! I-I'll shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.03,0:12:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.30,0:12:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.63,0:12:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Navy Captain "Axe-Hand" Morgan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.59,0:12:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! Kill him, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.76,0:13:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.02,0:13:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.66,0:13:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.15,0:13:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My pleasure, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.45,0:13:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The drawbridge stopped coming down?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.93,0:13:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare they get in our way?! Damn bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.07,0:13:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's doing this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.95,0:13:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not worry, Robin-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:14:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just trembling with anticipation!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.78,0:14:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will... rescue you for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.33,0:14:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a whole bunch of bad guys, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.08,0:14:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Scared" is written all over your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.26,0:14:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Me, scared?! I'm perfectly okay\Nwith lots of bad guys or whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.43,0:14:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm Captain Usopp,\Nbrave warrior of the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.26,0:14:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Dammit! This isn't a show!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.19,0:14:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are Klahadore's\Npirates we're dealing with!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.40,0:14:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'm scared! What's wrong with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.48,0:14:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want your sympathy!\NYou guys can leave! Leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.36,0:14:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We ain't laughing! We're helping\N'cause we think you're honorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.90,0:14:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if we'd risk our lives because of sympathy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.17,0:14:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... You guys...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.15,0:15:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.22,0:15:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.25,0:15:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... can't... move...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.60,0:15:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, even if you did catch up with Jango,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.77,0:15:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'd be no match for him anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.56,0:15:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way is probably safest for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.23,0:15:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I am no match...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.66,0:15:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I am no match for him...\NI will protect them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.06,0:15:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm captain of the Usopp Pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.33,0:15:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and a brave warrior of the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.89,0:15:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you lay a finger on the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.14,0:15:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What's with him?\N--He's yellin' somethin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.47,0:15:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Check it out, he's cryin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.80,0:16:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so funny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.40,0:16:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.12,0:16:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me and Usopp are gonna chase\Nthat hypno-freak! That a problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.52,0:16:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.40,0:16:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're one step too late, Haramaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.63,0:16:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't say so!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.88,0:16:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! That branch was in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.13,0:16:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.06,0:16:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Attack: Exploding Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.72,0:16:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you are taking to the ocean, Usopp-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.26,0:16:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I've decided to get going\Nbefore I start to change my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.57,0:16:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop me, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.75,0:16:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't. I could just tell somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.31,0:16:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's kind of sad, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.54,0:16:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next time I come to this village,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.88,0:17:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you adventure stories that\Nseem even more lie-like than lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.77,0:17:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I look forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.59,0:17:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys take care, too!\NLet's meet again sometime!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.71,0:17:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--How come?\N--Huh? How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.84,0:17:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you're antisocial...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.35,0:17:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be a pirate too, so we'll\Nmeet on the high seas eventually!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talkin' about? Get on already.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.58,0:17:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Eh?!\N--We're friends now, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.94,0:17:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get to be captain, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.38,0:17:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be dumb! I'm the captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.25,0:18:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, pirates! What're you\Nguys wasting time for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.61,0:18:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasting time? But the\Nbridge is only halfway down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.71,0:18:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Halfway is good enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.55,0:18:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be there in four seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.14,0:18:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jump with all your might towards the falls!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.25,0:18:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Granny? What does she mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.25,0:18:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. But she said\Njump towards the falls.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.80,0:18:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sound of the sea train?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's the meaning of that smile?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.28,0:18:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.24,0:18:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.11,0:18:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.04,0:18:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Straw Hat Theater"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.77,0:19:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Part 2"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.01,0:19:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A report on Luffy's eating habits\Nbefore Sanji joined the gang."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.14,0:19:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is "On-Location Tsubaki," a crooked\Nreporter who'll help us on this report.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.62,0:19:12.49,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"His favorite words:
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.51,0:19:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His favorite words are:\N"I'm so happy that words fail me."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.18,0:19:17.95,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"His favorite words:\N'I'm so happy that words fail me'"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.97,0:19:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Err... This is On-Location Tsubaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.85,0:19:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, you set sail all by yourself, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.45,0:19:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell everyone how an idiot like you survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.61,0:19:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.69,0:19:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took lots of meat and water that I got\Nin the village with me when I set sail.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.93,0:19:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I ate them all right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.75,0:19:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so dumbfounded that words fail me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.54,0:19:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, after that I was starving\Nand thirsty. It was really tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.71,0:19:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was saved by eating mushrooms\Nand stuff that someone left in the boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.31,0:19:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, the mushrooms just grew\Nbecause of the ample humidity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.27,0:19:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then, big fish would sometimes\Njump out of the sea, trying to eat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.73,0:19:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I beat them up and...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.31,0:19:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ate them?! You could've died.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.73,0:20:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like you were living hand to mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.23,0:20:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was okay! I had confidence in myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.98,0:20:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, hey... That's so\Npowerful that words fail me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.63,0:20:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Err... And then, that stupid\NZoro became a crew member.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.25,0:20:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I can't expect much from you, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.39,0:20:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You both are idiots. How were\Nyou able to make it this far?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.55,0:20:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set sail before he did,\Nso I was more experienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.64,0:20:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was used to sailing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.84,0:20:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our captain is like this, so I had\Nto be the one who got it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.41,0:20:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big fish would sometimes jump out of the sea,\Ntrying to eat us. So I beat them up and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.51,0:20:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been caught in the chains of\Ndisappointment and can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.68,0:20:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you could've\Nstarved to death then,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.72,0:20:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which could've led to the\Nend of your adventures, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.48,0:20:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. But if we had died, that would mean\Nwe weren't man enough to make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.44,0:20:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, hey... That's so manly that words fail me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.18,0:20:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then. Come on,\NNami the gangster woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, I was surprised by their lack\Nof planning or any sense of danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.60,0:21:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I managed the food\Nafter we set sail together...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.13,0:21:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...while being careful about properly preserving
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.66,0:21:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,cheese, bread, dried meat, etc. and water.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.88,0:21:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They might've died if it wasn't for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.99,0:21:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.68,0:21:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...they owe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.43,0:21:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, hey... That smile is so\Nscheming that words fail me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.57,0:21:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we have Usopp the scaredy-cat\Nwho was next to join the gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.00,0:21:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats finally got a bigger ship
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.27,0:21:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by obtaining the Going Merry when\Nyou left your village, didn't you,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.27,0:21:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even though you're all idiots?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.48,0:21:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I want them to\Nappreciate me for that first.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.68,0:21:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't you who gave it to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.62,0:21:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right. It was Kaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.87,0:21:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was because I was good\Nfriends with Kaya, wasn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.39,0:21:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna fight, do it later.\NDid something change in your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.99,0:21:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! Usopp is good at fishing,\Nso we ate quite a bit of fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.16,0:21:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the fish you catch,\Nlike sauries and sardines, are small.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.48,0:21:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dummy! I like seasonal fish\Nbetter than the meat of sea monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.56,0:21:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We had a kitchen, so I\Ncooked for you guys, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.60,0:21:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp's got lots of seasonings for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.46,0:22:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth, Nami's homemade\Nfood was quite good, but it wasn't free.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.75,0:22:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we never asked her to cook again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.37,0:22:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an expensive woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.39,0:22:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are devils everywhere in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.55,0:22:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, we finally have a damn filthy\Nman who always says "damn, damn."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.40,0:22:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I wanna cook just\Nfor Nami-san. My hobby is Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.69,0:22:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Sanji joined us,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.87,0:22:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,meals have become something\Nwe really look forward to.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.06,0:22:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we catch things like birds or fish,\Nhe'll turn them into really yummy food!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.51,0:22:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since he's a pro, he considers\Nnutritional balance, too, so that's helpful!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.13,0:22:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Mellorine! Mellorine! Love hurricane!\N--I was finally able to focus\Non my job as a navigator.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.93,0:22:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the only redeeming trait\Nyou have, so you can do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.77,0:22:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say, you bastard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.24,0:22:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, at any rate,\Nwhy don't I try telling everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.48,0:22:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how the food you eat\Nduring your journey tastes?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.55,0:23:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Words fail me...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.04,0:23:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a useless reporter!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.49,0:23:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin... It must've been really hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.14,0:23:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're not alone anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.59,0:23:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait, Robin. You've got us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.38,0:23:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So have faith in us... in Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.47,0:23:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll respond to your feelings without fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.34,0:23:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.98,0:23:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Bond of Friendship Woven\Nby Tears! Nami's World Map"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.81,0:23:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
